| 
| Ancestor class for type definitions known in the openEHR Expression formalism.
| 

abstract class EXPR_TYPE_DEF
    is_a Any

feature_group ("access")

    | 
    | Natural language type name of this type as used in abstract rules syntax variable
    | declarations.
    | 
    prop type_name: String;

    | 
    | Attribute of the openEHR primitive type (or Any) corresponding to this type definition
    | meta-type.
    | 
    prop type_anchor: Any;


end
